up this wedding!

65
00:03:43,765 --> 00:03:44,926
(chuckling) I don't think so.

66
00:03:47,269 --> 00:03:47,519
Oh yeah?

67
00:03:47,685 --> 00:03:49,445
Hm, I'm afraid that you
just weren't invited.

68
00:03:51,273 --> 00:03:52,273
(both yelling)

69
00:03:53,691 --> 00:03:54,193
What?

70
00:03:54,316 --> 00:03:55,796
I'll meet you in
Izumo, Princess Katy.

71
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,360
Very well, take care then.

72
