73
00:04:03,535 --> 00:04:04,535
Huh?

74
00:04:04,994 --> 00:04:05,994
Aaaah!

75
00:04:06,412 --> 00:04:07,412
(explosion)

76
00:04:09,331 --> 00:04:09,791
Katy!

77
00:04:09,958 --> 00:04:10,999
What are you trying to do?

78
00:04:12,544 --> 00:04:13,544
Momiji.

79
