people with your strange plants?

92
00:04:38,112 --> 00:04:39,112
But why?

93
00:04:40,239 --> 00:04:41,239
Why?

94
00:04:45,327 --> 00:04:46,327
(wind howls)

95
00:04:46,744 --> 00:04:47,744
That was my sister.

96
00:04:50,372 --> 00:04:52,572
Kusanagi, please tell me that
everything will be alright

97
00:04:54,086 --> 00:04:55,086
