429
00:21:04,345 --> 00:21:05,345
Oh my god, the light!

430
00:21:05,931 --> 00:21:06,931
The light!

431
00:21:08,559 --> 00:21:09,060
Nooo!

432
00:21:09,351 --> 00:21:10,351
(sobbing)

433
00:21:12,353 --> 00:21:13,434
