434
00:21:15,233 --> 00:21:16,513
Katy is no longer in this place.

435
00:21:18,359 --> 00:21:18,610
Go back!

436
00:21:18,819 --> 00:21:19,819
Go back to Tokyo!

437
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:25,950
(splashing)

438
00:21:28,579 --> 00:21:29,579
Kusanagi.

439
00:21:33,209 --> 00:21:34,209
Kusanagi.

440
00:21:34,918 --> 00:21:35,918
Kusanagi!

441
00:21:37,963 --> 00:21:38,963
(sobbing)

442
00:21:47,973 --> 00:21:48,973
Kusanagi, why?

443
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:50,600
What's happened to you?

444
00:21:51,392 --> 00:21:52,752
I keep calling your
name in my mind

445
00:21:53,478 --> 00:21:54,478
