450
00:22:06,367 --> 00:22:07,727
It's the next
episode of Blue Seed,

451
00:22:09,036 --> 00:22:10,036
number 22.

452
00:22:10,495 --> 00:22:11,495
Sadness,

453
00:22:12,039 --> 00:22:12,413
fate,

454
00:22:12,956 --> 00:22:13,956
Momiji Kushinada.

455
00:22:15,168 --> 00:22:16,488
